Package: savigesystemz
Version: 0.1.0
Section: web
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: nodejs (>= 20), libnotify-bin, xdg-utils, bash (>= 5)
Recommends: pnpm
Maintainer: Michael Spaulding <mtspaulding87@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://savigesystemz.com
Description: SavigeSystemZ desktop launcher
 Smart launcher for the SavigeSystemZ.com Next.js dev server. Resolves the
 repository on disk (SAVIGESYSTEMZ_REPO env or $HOME/.MyAppZ/SavigeSystemZ.com),
 acquires a single-instance lock to prevent duplicate processes, spawns
 pnpm dev:web on port 43907, waits for the port to bind, and opens the
 default browser. Useful for one-click local development sessions.
